extends layout

block content
    .container.py-5
      .row.mb-4
        .col
          h1.display-5.mb-2 Privacy Policy
          p.text-muted.mb-1 Last Updated: #[span.fw-semibold 2024-09-01]
          span.badge.bg-primary User Data & Security
      .row
        .col-lg-9
          .alert.alert-info.small.mb-4
            strong Note: 
            |  This summary is provided for transparency. It is not legal advice.
          .card.mb-4.shadow-sm
            .card-body
              h2.h5.mb-3 Overview
              p We are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains what we collect, why we collect it, how we store and secure it, and the rights you have.
              p.mb-0 If you have questions, contact us at #[code privacy@example.com].

          .card.mb-4
            .card-body
              h2.h6.text-uppercase.fw-bold.mb-3 Data Categories (Summary)
              .table-responsive
                table.table.table-sm.table-striped.align-middle
                  thead
                    tr
                      th(scope="col") Category
                      th(scope="col") Examples
                      th(scope="col") Purpose
                      th(scope="col") Retention
                  tbody
                    tr
                      td Account
                      td Username, email
                      td Authentication, communication
                      td While account is active
                    tr
                      td Security
                      td Login timestamps, hashed password
                      td Protect service, detect abuse
                      td Rolling logs (min needed)
                    tr
                      td Usage
                      td Page views, feature use
                      td Improve functionality
                      td Aggregated after analysis
                    tr
                      td Optional
                      td Profile preferences
                      td Personalization
                      td Until removed by user

          h2.h5.mt-5.mb-3 Details
          #policy-accordion.accordion.mb-5
            .accordion-item
              h2.accordion-header
                button.accordion-button.collapsed(type="button", data-bs-toggle="collapse", data-bs-target="#c1") 1. Data We Collect
              #c1.accordion-collapse.collapse(data-bs-parent="#policy-accordion")
                .accordion-body
                  p We collect only the minimum data required to operate and improve the service.
                  ul.mb-2
                    li Account data (email, username)
                    li Authentication artifacts (secure password hash, tokens)
                    li Basic technical metadata (IP (short-lived), user agent, timestamps)
                    li Usage metrics (aggregated and anonymized where possible)
                  p No sensitive categories (e.g., health, biometric) are intentionally collected.

            .accordion-item
              h2.accordion-header
                button.accordion-button.collapsed(type="button", data-bs-toggle="collapse", data-bs-target="#c2") 2. Legal Basis / Purpose
              #c2.accordion-collapse.collapse(data-bs-parent="#policy-accordion")
                .accordion-body
                  p Purposes include:
                  ul
                    li Provide core functionality (login, account management)
                    li Maintain security and prevent fraud
                    li Improve performance and user experience
                    li Comply with applicable legal obligations
                  p Where required, we rely on consent or legitimate interest (balanced and documented).

            .accordion-item
              h2.accordion-header
                button.accordion-button.collapsed(type="button", data-bs-toggle="collapse", data-bs-target="#c3") 3. Storage & Security
              #c3.accordion-collapse.collapse(data-bs-parent="#policy-accordion")
                .accordion-body
                  p All user data is stored in a secured database with:
                  ul
                    li Access control (least privilege)
                    li Encrypted transport (HTTPS / TLS)
                    li Secure password hashing (industry-standard algorithm; never stored in plain text)
                    li Regular dependency updates and vulnerability monitoring
                  p Backups are encrypted and retained only for disaster recovery within limited rotation windows.

            .accordion-item
              h2.accordion-header
                button.accordion-button.collapsed(type="button", data-bs-toggle="collapse", data-bs-target="#c4") 4. Data Minimization & Retention
              #c4.accordion-collapse.collapse(data-bs-parent="#policy-accordion")
                .accordion-body
                  p We retain personal data only as long as necessary for the purposes outlined. Inactive or deleted accounts trigger scheduled cleanup tasks.
                  p Aggregated analytics are kept without direct identifiers.

            .accordion-item
              h2.accordion-header
                button.accordion-button.collapsed(type="button", data-bs-toggle="collapse", data-bs-target="#c5") 5. Sharing & Disclosure
              #c5.accordion-collapse.collapse(data-bs-parent="#policy-accordion")
                .accordion-body
                  p We do not sell personal data.
                  p Limited sharing may occur with:
                  ul
                    li Infrastructure or email service providers (only essential data)
                    li Security / monitoring services (pseudonymized where feasible)
                  p Legal disclosure occurs only when required by law with appropriate review.

            .accordion-item
              h2.accordion-header
                button.accordion-button.collapsed(type="button", data-bs-toggle="collapse", data-bs-target="#c6") 6. Cookies & Tracking
              #c6.accordion-collapse.collapse(data-bs-parent="#policy-accordion")
                .accordion-body
                  p We use strictly necessary cookies for session management. Optional analytics or preference cookies (if enabled) are disclosed via a banner or settings panel.
                  p You can disable non-essential cookies in your browser or any provided preference center.

            .accordion-item
              h2.accordion-header
                button.accordion-button.collapsed(type="button", data-bs-toggle="collapse", data-bs-target="#c7") 7. Your Rights
              #c7.accordion-collapse.collapse(data-bs-parent="#policy-accordion")
                .accordion-body
                  p Subject to jurisdiction, you may have rights to:
                  ul
                    li Access a copy of your personal data
                    li Request correction or deletion
                    li Restrict or object to certain processing
                    li Data portability (structured, common format)
                  p Contact us to exercise rights. Identity verification may be required.

            .accordion-item
              h2.accordion-header
                button.accordion-button.collapsed(type="button", data-bs-toggle="collapse", data-bs-target="#c8") 8. International Transfers
              #c8.accordion-collapse.collapse(data-bs-parent="#policy-accordion")
                .accordion-body
                  p Where data leaves your region, safeguards (e.g., standard contractual clauses) are applied.

            .accordion-item
              h2.accordion-header
                button.accordion-button.collapsed(type="button", data-bs-toggle="collapse", data-bs-target="#c9") 9. Changes to This Policy
              #c9.accordion-collapse.collapse(data-bs-parent="#policy-accordion")
                .accordion-body
                  p We may update this policy. Material changes will be highlighted or communicated through in-app notice.
                  p Continued use after an update indicates acceptance.

            .accordion-item
              h2.accordion-header
                button.accordion-button.collapsed(type="button", data-bs-toggle="collapse", data-bs-target="#c10") 10. Contact
              #c10.accordion-collapse.collapse(data-bs-parent="#policy-accordion")
                .accordion-body
                  p For privacy inquiries or rights requests:
                  ul
                    li Email: #[code privacy@example.com]
                    li Subject: "Privacy Request"
                  p We aim to respond within 30 days.

          .mb-4
            small.text-muted This document is provided for transparency and does not create contractual obligations beyond applicable law.

        .col-lg-3
          .position-sticky(style="top:2rem")
            .card.mb-3
              .card-header.fw-semibold Quick Nav
              .list-group.list-group-flush.small
                a.list-group-item(href="#c1") Data We Collect
                a.list-group-item(href="#c3") Storage & Security
                a.list-group-item(href="#c4") Retention
                a.list-group-item(href="#c5") Sharing
                a.list-group-item(href="#c7") Your Rights
                a.list-group-item(href="#c10") Contact
            .card
              .card-body
                h6.mb-2 Need Help?
                p.mb-2 If you see inaccurate info, contact support.
                a.btn.btn-outline-primary.btn-sm(href="/support") Go to Support

